{"cid":"1665953433364487","cha_name":"拳皇直播","desc":"美国波士顿，能够进入异次元解封八歧大蛇的三神器八尺琼勾玉、八咫镜和草稚剑正在展出，中情局特工不知火舞正从八神家族传人八神庵处打探三神器的秘密，岂料卢卡尔抢走三神器抢走并躲入了异次元。\n神乐家族传人千鹤透露被抢走的草雉剑为假，委托不知火舞向草稚家族求助。卢卡尔抢走神器后诱骗KOF大赛的格斗家们进入异次元，意欲成为拳皇。\n同时不知火舞和八神庵邀请草稚京一同出战打败卢卡尔。中情局为了调查这起异次元中的犯罪行为亦派出探员特瑞与不知火舞等人一起进入异次元。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1665953433364487","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p9.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_token":false,"fb_ex {"cid":"1661986683079688","cha_name":"大话西游直播","desc":"至尊宝（周星驰饰）被月光宝盒带回到五百年前，遇见紫霞仙子（朱茵饰），被对方打上烙印成为了对方的人，并发觉自己已变成孙悟空。\n紫霞与青霞（朱茵饰）本是如来佛祖座前日月神灯的灯芯（白天是紫霞，晚上是青霞），二人虽然同一肉身却仇恨颇深，因此紫霞立下誓言，谁能拔出她手中的紫青宝剑，谁就是她的意中人。\n紫青宝剑被至尊宝于不经意间拔出，紫霞决定以身相许，却遭一心记挂白晶晶（莫文蔚饰）的至尊宝拒绝。后牛魔王（陆树铭饰）救下迷失在沙漠中的紫霞，并逼紫霞与他成婚，关键时刻，至尊宝现身。","schema":"aweme://aweme/challenge/detail?cid=1661986683079688","author":{"uid":"6796248446","short_id":"52","nickname":"抖音小助手","gender":1,"signature":"本宝宝暂时还没想到个性签名","avatar_larger":{"uri":"1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p6.douyinpic.com/aweme/1080x1080/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_thumb":{"uri":"100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/100x100/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"avatar_medium":{"uri":"720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c","url_list":["https://p29.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p3.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474","https://p26.douyinpic.com/aweme/720x720/312f4000941e3f5577e3c.jpeg?from=273881474"],"width":720,"height":720},"birthday":"","is_verified":true,"follow_status":0,"aweme_count":0,"following_count":0,"follower_count":0,"favoriting_count":0,"total_favorited":0,"is_block":false,"hide_search":true,"constellation":10,"location":"","hide_location":false,"weibo_verify":"","custom_verify":"","unique_id":"douyin","bind_phone":"","special_lock":0,"need_recommend":0,"is_binded_weibo":false,"weibo_name":"","weibo_schema":"","weibo_url":"","story_open":false,"story_count":0,"has_facebook_token":false,"has_twitter_tok user.signature: 我从小在洪湖边上长大，因为1996年长大水，也就是因为那次大水没办法上学了，家里条件又太差就辍学了、从那以后父母教会了我一些养家的生存技能、时间过的很快，父亲18年前就生病去世了，我也有了自己的家，有了3个可爱的闺女、老公之前是在外地修车的，为了孩子们能多一下些陪伴，就回家创业了！希望大家多多支持我们一下啊！❤️
